/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a pedestrian's viewpoint on the sidewalk, immersing the viewer in the city's daily life. The street is lined with lush green trees, their leaves rustling gently in the breeze, providing a stark contrast to the clear blue sky above. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the street, their facades bathed in the soft glow of the setting sun. The sun's rays filter through the leaves of the trees, casting dappled shadows on the pavement. The image is taken from a low angle, which enhances the grandeur of the buildings and the vastness of the sky.
